guage:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">电子式：通过电路板上的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">IC</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">芯片来控制烘烤设置，通过液晶屏幕或发光二极管来显示操作设置的电烤箱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">随处都可以吃到烧烤的食物，为什么要在家里使用烤箱作烘烤食物？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">首先，木碳会产生大量灰尘和油烟，并且明火烤会增加导致癌症的几率，严重影响身体健康。其次，在小摊上不能保证食物来源是否清洁卫生。在家里，食物的口味、花样均可以随心所欲，食物的质量能够有充分的保证并且经济，时间也不受限制。所以只有自己使用烤箱制作自己想吃的多种食物，才能让自己做的开心吃的放心，充分享受烘烤美食的乐趣，给家人多一份惊喜。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333;\r\nmso-ansi-la